      "content": "The Lucidworks AI Platform API exposes prediction endpoints for FAQ enrichment, keyword extraction, named entity recognition (NER), retrieval augmented generation (RAG), summarization, passthrough LLM calls, and standalone query rewriting. Predictions are submitted by use case and fetched asynchronously by prediction ID.\n\nContact Support:\n Name: Lucidworks Support",
